{"tid":1275708,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普稱香港人追求民主","createTime":"2019-07-01T21:59:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T22:04:32.000Z","uid":4783,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4f52637aeb13a1579402c80a47cfb299505eaaba","tid":1275708,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T21:59:21.000Z","msg":"2019-07-02 HKT 05:27<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，香港人追求民主。<br />\n<br />\n另外，美國國務院促請香港各方避免使用暴力。<br />\n<br />\n國務院發言人回應香港示威者闖入立法會時，促請各方避免使用暴力。<br />\n<br />\n發言人表示，香港成功在於法治以及尊重基本權利，包括自由表達及和平集會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466140-20190702.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466140-20190702.htm&d=9Ou39NWu4C7Ce3sh0Mn9CznF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=8d481851\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1466140-20190702.htm&h=252b4767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1466140-20190702.htm</a>"},{"pid":"8f4ef96c9b95f4391b007494f2246d576d71237f","tid":1275708,"uid":11598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:00:14.000Z","msg":"他在白宮回應示威者闖入立法會時表示，相信香港人追求民主，大部分人追求民主，但有政府不要民主。特朗普強調，示威關乎民主。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，對香港的動盪感到哀傷。"},{"pid":"6b6bd00071a0d3e14acb34b2180fdd6c84fdebcd","tid":1275708,"uid":11598,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:01:56.000Z","msg":"林奠：痛心 震驚 暴力<br />\n侵：哀傷<br />\n<br />\n邊個愛民 高下立見"},{"pid":"8dd2f1ec332fdb9e5f04181e1b9a7fb3b9e79c25","tid":1275708,"uid":25601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b6bd00071a0d3e14acb34b2180fdd6c84fdebcd","tid":1275708,"uid":11598,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:01:56.000Z","msg":"林奠：痛心 震驚 暴力<br />\n侵：哀傷<br />\n<br />\n邊個愛民 高下立見"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T22:04:32.000Z","msg":"林鄭多表示d<br />\ntrump表示wfc"}]}